    <briefdescription>
<para>Executor for multidraw calls. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class is used to pass multidraw buffers to a draw call. It could be constructed only by <ref refid="classMultidrawContext" kindref="compound">MultidrawContext</ref>. It is used to hide multidraw buffers from a user. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
